# Notion3D 项目约定

- 产品定位：**ForgeCAD 装配工作台**（描述 → 建模 → 预览 → 导出 STL / parts）
- 标准架构：Engine `apps/api` + MCP `apps/mcp-server` + Web `apps/web` + `apps/agent-bridge`
- 架构文档：[docs/architecture.md](../../docs/architecture.md)
- **Agent 集成**：MCP（`notion3d_render_forge`）；Web 对话 `POST .../turn` → Adapter
- 调试：`make dev` | `make dev WEB_TURN=bridge|gateway`
- 设计流水线：[docs/design-pipeline.md](../../docs/design-pipeline.md)
- 运行模式自检：[docs/dev-modes.md](../../docs/dev-modes.md)
